    "description": "We at Mapei India are looking for an experienced Process Engineer based out of Srinagar. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Mapei India:\nMapei India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mapei India!",
